1
00:05:31,372 --> 00:05:34,958
BLAlR: Welcome, Colonel Lee.
Welcome to my home.

2
00:05:35,335 --> 00:05:38,170
Make yourself comfortable
there, colonel.

3
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:48,513
Allow me to get to the point, sir.

4
00:05:48,681 --> 00:05:51,933
l have been authorized by
President Lincoln himself. . .

5
00:05:52,101 --> 00:05:55,103
. ..with the full blessing
of the War Department...

6
00:05:55,271 --> 00:06:00,025
